         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Adelaide, 23/3/80. ¶ Dear Sir Ferdinand, ¶  ¶ Thanks for your suggestion regarding the sowing of  ¶ Acacia ¶   ¶ decurrens ¶  on the bare places of our Reserves. I will adopt your recommendation and t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">80.03.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From J. Ednie Brown</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">GRG 16/3/1 Conservator of Forests letter press copy book, p. 387, Woods and Forests Department, State Records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Adelaide, 23/3/80.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir Ferdinand,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Thanks for your suggestion regarding the sowing of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Acacia</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">decurrens</hi>
               </seg> on the bare places of our Reserves. I will adopt your recommendation and try the experiment this season now approaching.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>To whom can I apply for seed? I will take 10 lbs (ten pounds) weight of it. What is the best method of preparing the seed previous to sowing? How many hours should it be soaked in water, and how hot should the water, be? Some information on these points will be thankfully received</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I purpose having another look for E. <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Cosmophylla</hi>
               </seg> one of these days.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. E. Brown</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir Ferd. Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Govt. Botanist,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
